title: SIC! SIC! SIC!
html:
SIC! SIC! SIC!

“One of nine women will get breast cancer as well as many men.” [From the Los Angeles Times, 30 August 1992, page E7. Submitted by Sylvia Bursztyn, Van Nuys.]
